data.description: Captivating resale Cullers Home located in the Loma Del Este subdivision, CLEAN and ready to move in! Open floor plan offers 3 bedrooms and two full bathrooms. Kitchen and living space are perfect for your gatherings and family to enjoy. You will encounter custom tile designs in the MB bathroom including double sinks, granite countertops 3cm solid on all tops/Deep soaker tub & accent glass mosaic. Mb has insulated wall for sound control. Kitchen has granite counter tops, Alder cabinets with crown molding and deco travertine backsplash. Plantation shutters are 4' throughout. All Pella windows, tankless water heater. Hand textured on all walls and ceilings, 8 foot front & back doors, and base moldings. So many things to mention. There is a community Park  you can walk to, nearby shopping centers, easy access to  Loop 375. Call today to schedule your appointment.
